      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ranged Tactics Toolbox pg. 20</em><br/><strong>Price</strong> <img src=\"https://www.aonprd.com/images/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\" title=\"PFS Legal\"/> 25 gp (common), <img src=\"https://www.aonprd.com/images/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\" title=\"PFS Legal\"/> 100 gp (masterwork); <strong>Weight</strong> 2 lbs. (common), 2 lbs. (masterwork)</p><h2 class=\"framing\">Description</h2><p>This foot-long brass funnel amplifies sounds entering through the broad end for anyone listening at the narrow end. The listener gains a +2 circumstance bonus on sound-based Perception checks but must use one hand to hold the trumpet to the ear in order to gain the benefit. A masterwork ear trumpet's exquisite acoustic properties grant the listener a +4 circumstance bonus instead.</p>",
